<D>__{we're awfully quiet tonight.}
<A>__{the group remains silent. lawford and george exchange a glance. skipper catches it.}
<C>__{skipper}
<D>__{something on your mind, george?}
<A>__{george looks up and wipes his mouth with a napkin.}
