<D>__{what do you mean?}
<C>__{lawford}
<D>__{he's been beyond the reach. to the edge of the abyss and back. he'll do well by us all george. he's a real salt. there's no malice in him and there's nothing more dear to him than his boys. so sleep well my friend.}
